{
    "publish_date": "2010-11-17T05:20:56.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT3M48S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "OK, let&#39;s say you&#39;re me,\nand you&#39;re in math class.", 
            "dur": "2.202", 
            "start": "0.58"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You&#39;re supposed to be learning\nabout exponential functions,", 
            "dur": "2.458", 
            "start": "2.782"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but you&#39;re having trouble caring\nabout exponential functions", 
            "dur": "2.63", 
            "start": "5.24"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because, unfortunately, your\nmath class is probably not", 
            "dur": "2.7", 
            "start": "7.87"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "terribly engaging.", 
            "dur": "1.764", 
            "start": "10.57"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You&#39;re supposed to be drawing\nand labeling some axes", 
            "dur": "2.166", 
            "start": "12.334"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so that you can graph this\ny equals 2 to the x thing.", 
            "dur": "2.42", 
            "start": "14.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And your teacher seems to think\nthat drawing and labeling axes", 
            "dur": "2.7", 
            "start": "16.92"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is the very essence\nof mathematics.", 
            "dur": "2.45", 
            "start": "19.62"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But you&#39;re bored and can&#39;t\nhelp but wonder, why?", 
            "dur": "4.04", 
            "start": "22.07"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So you do what any\nconscientious student", 
            "dur": "1.7", 
            "start": "26.11"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "would do in this situation\nand start doodling.", 
            "dur": "1.92", 
            "start": "27.81"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And because you&#39;re me, you like\nto play games with yourself", 
            "dur": "2.458", 
            "start": "29.73"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "when you doodle.", 
            "dur": "0.762", 
            "start": "32.188"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Here&#39;s one game.", 
            "dur": "0.86", 
            "start": "32.95"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You&#39;re drawing a line.", 
            "dur": "1.032", 
            "start": "33.81"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But when it crosses\none of the blue lines", 
            "dur": "1.708", 
            "start": "34.842"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "one your little piece of paper,\nit splits into two lines.", 
            "dur": "2.68", 
            "start": "36.55"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Maybe this line is like the\nneck of a mythical hydra, where", 
            "dur": "2.86", 
            "start": "39.23"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "every time one of its heads\ngets chopped off by a blue line,", 
            "dur": "3.06", 
            "start": "42.09"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it grows two more in its place.", 
            "dur": "2.051", 
            "start": "45.15"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You want to see if you\ncan get all the way", 
            "dur": "1.749", 
            "start": "47.201"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to the bottom of the\npage following this rule", 
            "dur": "1.874", 
            "start": "48.95"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because, if you do, then you\ncan draw all of the little hydra", 
            "dur": "2.956", 
            "start": "50.824"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "heads at the end.", 
            "dur": "1.106", 
            "start": "53.78"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But you don&#39;t get very\nfar on your first try.", 
            "dur": "1.874", 
            "start": "54.886"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You decide to try again,\nthis time spacing things out", 
            "dur": "2.19", 
            "start": "56.76"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a little more at the beginning.", 
            "dur": "1.1", 
            "start": "58.95"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Unfortunately,\nthings are filling", 
            "dur": "1.374", 
            "start": "60.05"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "up fast, though you got\nfarther than last time.", 
            "dur": "2.42", 
            "start": "61.424"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Maybe if you have\nmore room, or maybe", 
            "dur": "1.541", 
            "start": "63.844"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "if you sharpen your\npencil more, you", 
            "dur": "1.38", 
            "start": "65.385"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "can get to the\nbottom of the page.", 
            "dur": "1.416", 
            "start": "66.765"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Oh, and don&#39;t forget to\ndraw and label your axes.", 
            "dur": "2.319", 
            "start": "68.181"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If each broad swing of\nHercules&#39;s sword chops", 
            "dur": "2.192", 
            "start": "70.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "off all the heads, that&#39;s\ndoubling your number.", 
            "dur": "1.958", 
            "start": "72.692"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, you can see\nwhere I&#39;m going.", 
            "dur": "1.64", 
            "start": "74.65"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m not going to try\nand teach you math,", 
            "dur": "1.39", 
            "start": "76.29"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "just how to wield it\nfor doodling purposes.", 
            "dur": "1.791", 
            "start": "77.68"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In this case, that&#39;s going\nto be a lot of heads.", 
            "dur": "2.729", 
            "start": "79.471"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Good luck Hercules.", 
            "dur": "1.64", 
            "start": "82.2"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But maybe drawing binary\ntrees all straight like that", 
            "dur": "2.486", 
            "start": "83.84"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is not an interesting\nenough game", 
            "dur": "1.374", 
            "start": "86.326"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to hold your attention for long.", 
            "dur": "1.333", 
            "start": "87.7"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So you start drawing\nthem in arbitrary shapes.", 
            "dur": "2.107", 
            "start": "89.033"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Or less arbitrary shapes.", 
            "dur": "1.68", 
            "start": "91.14"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Maybe you start drawing a binary\ntree that looks like a tree.", 
            "dur": "3.121", 
            "start": "92.82"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And maybe you can&#39;t see this\ntree in very high quality", 
            "dur": "2.249", 
            "start": "95.941"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because your camera, much\nlike your math class,", 
            "dur": "1.958", 
            "start": "98.19"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is fuzzy, unfocused, and\naltogether not very good.", 
            "dur": "3.082", 
            "start": "100.148"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Maybe you change\nthe rules slightly", 
            "dur": "1.66", 
            "start": "103.23"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and make a ternary bush, where\neach branch sprouts three more", 
            "dur": "2.97", 
            "start": "104.89"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "branches.", 
            "dur": "0.77", 
            "start": "107.86"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Unfortunately, your math\nclass is 45 minutes long,", 
            "dur": "3.41", 
            "start": "108.63"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and soon you need a more\ninteresting doodle game.", 
            "dur": "2.529", 
            "start": "112.04"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So you go back to the game\nwhere your line splits", 
            "dur": "2.041", 
            "start": "114.569"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "at every level, only\nthis time, instead", 
            "dur": "1.74", 
            "start": "116.61"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of trying to squish\nall the lines in,", 
            "dur": "1.93", 
            "start": "118.35"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you let them hit each other.", 
            "dur": "1.99", 
            "start": "120.28"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And when they crash,\nthere&#39;s a fiery explosion,", 
            "dur": "2.29", 
            "start": "122.27"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the crashing lines end.", 
            "dur": "1.79", 
            "start": "124.56"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There.", 
            "dur": "1.57", 
            "start": "126.35"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Maybe you turn your\nnotebook sideways", 
            "dur": "1.55", 
            "start": "127.92"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "so that you can make sure you&#39;re\ngetting the horizontal spacing", 
            "dur": "2.24", 
            "start": "129.47"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "right.", 
            "dur": "0.77", 
            "start": "131.71"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Maybe, to go back to\nmythology, Hercules", 
            "dur": "2.06", 
            "start": "132.48"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "has a method where,\ninstead of cauterizing", 
            "dur": "1.75", 
            "start": "134.54"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the necks of the Hydra to\nkeep them from growing back,", 
            "dur": "2.89", 
            "start": "136.29"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "he&#39;s found that the necks stick\ntogether if they get too close.", 
            "dur": "3.11", 
            "start": "139.18"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And instead of\ngrowing new heads,", 
            "dur": "1.51", 
            "start": "142.29"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they just fill up with blood.", 
            "dur": "2.31", 
            "start": "143.8"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It might seem a little\nmorbid for math class,", 
            "dur": "1.97", 
            "start": "146.11"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but maybe if the curriculum\nwasn&#39;t so appalling,", 
            "dur": "2.86", 
            "start": "148.08"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the teaching methods\nweren&#39;t so atrocious,", 
            "dur": "2.655", 
            "start": "150.94"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you wouldn&#39;t have to\nentertain yourself", 
            "dur": "1.625", 
            "start": "153.595"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with these stories and games.", 
            "dur": "1.907", 
            "start": "155.22"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Speaking of this doodle game,\nsomething very interesting", 
            "dur": "2.333", 
            "start": "157.127"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is happening.", 
            "dur": "1.23", 
            "start": "159.46"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Looks like your simple rules\nabout splitting and crashing", 
            "dur": "2.49", 
            "start": "160.69"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "are creating\nSierpinski&#39;s triangle,", 
            "dur": "1.82", 
            "start": "163.18"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which is a pretty\nawesome fractal.", 
            "dur": "1.676", 
            "start": "165"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But the point is not to\nlearn about fractals,", 
            "dur": "1.874", 
            "start": "166.676"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or cellular automata,\nor Sierpinski,", 
            "dur": "1.969", 
            "start": "168.55"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but to show that\nsimple doodle games can", 
            "dur": "1.666", 
            "start": "170.519"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "lead to mathematical results\nso cool and beautiful", 
            "dur": "3.065", 
            "start": "172.185"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that they&#39;re famous.", 
            "dur": "1.35", 
            "start": "175.25"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "At least, famous\nto people like me.", 
            "dur": "2.39", 
            "start": "176.6"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And if you&#39;re good at\ninventing doodle games,", 
            "dur": "1.99", 
            "start": "178.99"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you might even end up\ndoing some real mathematics", 
            "dur": "2.53", 
            "start": "180.98"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "during your math class.", 
            "dur": "2.12", 
            "start": "183.51"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Anyway, maybe you don&#39;t\ncare about accuracy.", 
            "dur": "2.68", 
            "start": "185.63"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Maybe you try the\ngame again, only", 
            "dur": "1.48", 
            "start": "188.31"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you don&#39;t keep track of spacing,\nand when you make a mistake", 
            "dur": "2.22", 
            "start": "189.79"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and accidentally grow heads\nwhere you shouldn&#39;t, you just", 
            "dur": "2.374", 
            "start": "192.01"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "roll with it.", 
            "dur": "1.536", 
            "start": "194.384"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now you&#39;ve introduced an\nelement of random error,", 
            "dur": "2.3", 
            "start": "195.92"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and you want to know how this\nwill affect the final picture.", 
            "dur": "2.54", 
            "start": "198.22"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It still looks like a\npretty awesome doodle", 
            "dur": "1.62", 
            "start": "200.76"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and has many of\nthe same elements,", 
            "dur": "1.416", 
            "start": "202.38"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "though it lacks the structure.", 
            "dur": "1.804", 
            "start": "203.796"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Speaking of the structure, maybe\nbecause you&#39;re really, super", 
            "dur": "2.79", 
            "start": "205.6"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "bored, and your class is\nseemingly never going to end,", 
            "dur": "3.75", 
            "start": "208.39"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you start looking at the\nnumber of necks at each level", 
            "dur": "2.55", 
            "start": "212.14"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and trying to figure\nout the pattern.", 
            "dur": "2.17", 
            "start": "214.69"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Maybe you haven&#39;t forgotten\nabout powers of two.", 
            "dur": "3.032", 
            "start": "216.86"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Anyway, I hope I&#39;ve\nprovided you with something", 
            "dur": "1.958", 
            "start": "219.892"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "entertaining to do\nnext time you&#39;re bored.", 
            "dur": "2.37", 
            "start": "221.85"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Good luck with your math class.", 
            "dur": "2.29", 
            "start": "224.22"
        }
    ], 
